**Description :**
```
@defer (on timer(10s)) 
{ 
  <app-box-five></app-box-five> 
}

```

After waiting 10 seconds, I checked the network tab in the browser and noticed that app.component.ts was lazy-loaded instead of box-five.component.ts.

I expected that only box-five.component.ts would be lazy-loaded.

Could you please explain why this behavior occurred?
